{"tid":748786,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美國《每日秀》主持人稱「非洲」贏了世界盃被批種族歧視","createTime":"2018-07-19T13:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T14:23:52.000Z","uid":124292,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a066a54f042d9b11c428bacfc8151bfbbd8e1d","tid":748786,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"星期天，法國4-2擊敗克羅地亞贏得2018年俄羅斯世界盃的冠軍。南非喜劇演員特雷弗-諾亞在自己節目《每日秀》上聲稱世界盃的勝利是屬於非洲的。<br />\n<br />\n諾亞在星期一的節目上說道：「非洲贏了世界盃。我理解，他們得說這是法國隊。但是你看看這些傢伙，我的朋友，你不會在法國南部閒逛時，被那裏的陽光曬得這樣黑吧。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果你不理解，基本上，法國隊是非洲人的後備隊。一旦塞內加爾和尼日利亞被淘汰出局，他們就是我們所支持的。」<br />\n<br />\n這番言論引發軒然大波，法國隊球迷紛紛在推特上批評諾亞。其中法國前真人秀電視台明星Martin Medus 抨擊道：「你這個f***種族主義分子。他們是法國人，某些傻子總是要提起一下他們的背景。他們已經很努力的告訴人們自己是令人驕傲的法國人了，你還不尊敬的稱呼他們是非洲人。湖人隊是非洲籃球隊嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5966249/Daily-host-Trevor-Noah-accused-racism-joking-Africa-won-World-Cup.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5966249%2FDaily-host-Trevor-Noah-accused-racism-joking-Africa-won-World-Cup.html&d=7G2Q%2F4EZf98l197n22WH5pnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=a65c60dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5966249/Daily-host-Trevor-Noah-accused-racism-joking-Africa-won-World-Cup.html</a>"},{"pid":"79061d135dc9327b26c702c14105df278eb4b575","tid":748786,"uid":20473,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"你還不尊敬的稱呼他們是非洲人。湖人隊是非洲籃球隊嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢句先最歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8984312b56d4986573966be3be4f578deb0c954","tid":748786,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79061d135dc9327b26c702c14105df278eb4b575","tid":748786,"uid":20473,"like":15,"dislike":0,"s